WEBVTT

00:01:46.860 --> 00:01:48.061
( Eugeo gasps )

00:01:52.431 --> 00:01:55.068
Bercouli: THERE. NOW I'M READY.

00:01:55.134 --> 00:01:56.636
( Eugeo gasps )

00:01:56.703 --> 00:02:00.674
Bercouli: ALL RIGHT, KID,
BEFORE WE GET INTO IT,

00:02:00.740 --> 00:02:03.643
THERE'S SOMETHING
I WANNA ASK YOU.

00:02:03.710 --> 00:02:04.544
Eugeo: WHAT?

00:02:04.611 --> 00:02:06.946
Bercouli: YOU DIDN'T, YOU KNOW,

00:02:07.013 --> 00:02:11.217
KILL VICE COMMANDER FANATIO,
DID YOU?

00:02:11.284 --> 00:02:13.520
Eugeo: SHE'S ALIVE.

00:02:13.587 --> 00:02:16.022
SHE'S BEING HEALED AS WE SPEAK.

00:02:16.089 --> 00:02:17.290
( Bercouli sighs )

00:02:17.356 --> 00:02:18.758
THAT'S GOOD.

00:02:18.825 --> 00:02:20.193
SINCE YOU SPARED HER LIFE,

00:02:20.259 --> 00:02:22.962
I'LL RETURN THE FAVOR
AND SPARE YOURS.

00:02:23.029 --> 00:02:24.631
( Eugeo gasps )

00:02:24.698 --> 00:02:26.633
HOW DISRESPECTFUL.

00:02:26.700 --> 00:02:28.067
( Bercouli chuckles )

00:02:28.134 --> 00:02:29.669
WHY DO YOU THINK THAT?

00:02:29.736 --> 00:02:32.872
Eugeo: IF YOU'RE THIS HIGH UP
IN THE CATHEDRAL,

00:02:32.939 --> 00:02:36.075
YOU MUST BE THE COMMANDER
OF THE INTEGRITY KNIGHTS.

00:02:36.142 --> 00:02:38.277
Bercouli: YEAH, WHAT IF I AM?

00:02:39.245 --> 00:02:40.880
Eugeo: WHAT ABOUT THE OTHERS?!

00:02:40.947 --> 00:02:42.716
FANATIO ISN'T THE ONLY KNIGHT!

00:02:42.782 --> 00:02:47.286
ELDRIE, THE FOUR
WHIRLING BLADES, ALICE...

00:02:47.353 --> 00:02:50.456
WHAT ABOUT THEM?!
DON'T THEY MATTER?!

00:02:50.524 --> 00:02:53.192
Bercouli: I SEE.
YOU'RE TAKING THAT ROAD.

00:02:53.259 --> 00:02:55.494
HOW DO I PUT THIS?

00:02:55.562 --> 00:02:57.897
ELDRIE IS ALICE'S APPRENTICE.

00:02:57.964 --> 00:02:59.332
THE FOUR WHIRLING BLADES‐‐

00:02:59.398 --> 00:03:02.769
DAKIRA, JACE,
HOVEREN, AND GEERO‐‐

00:03:02.836 --> 00:03:04.403
THEY'RE FANATIO'S.

00:03:04.470 --> 00:03:07.874
AND HER? WELL,
SHE HAPPENS TO BE MY APPRENTICE.

00:03:07.941 --> 00:03:11.077
IT'S NOT THAT I
DON'T CARE ABOUT THE OTHERS.

00:03:11.144 --> 00:03:14.280
IT'S JUST
I'M INVESTED IN FANATIO.

00:03:14.347 --> 00:03:18.317
THAT'S WHY, IF YOU KILLED HER,
I'D BE OBLIGED TO AVENGE HER.

00:03:18.384 --> 00:03:20.253
THAT'S ALL THERE IS TO IT.

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:23.322
( chuckles ) THOUGH,
NOW THAT I THINK ABOUT IT,

00:03:23.389 --> 00:03:26.760
I GUESS LITTLE ALICE DOES
LOOK UP TO ME AS HER MENTOR.

00:03:26.826 --> 00:03:30.163
SHE'S NOT THE SAME
AS SHE WAS SIX YEARS AGO,

00:03:30.229 --> 00:03:32.532
WHEN SHE FIRST BECAME
AN APPRENTICE KNIGHT.

00:03:32.599 --> 00:03:35.268
IF ME AND HER WENT AT IT NOW,

00:03:35.334 --> 00:03:37.571
I DON'T KNOW
WHO'D COME OUT ON TOP.

00:03:37.637 --> 00:03:39.038
( Eugeo gasps )

00:03:39.105 --> 00:03:43.009
Bercouli: ANYWAY, SEEING AS HOW
ALICE IS AS STRONG AS ME,

00:03:43.076 --> 00:03:45.344
YOU MUST HAVE
SNUCK PAST HER SOMEHOW,

00:03:45.411 --> 00:03:48.347
BUT YOU WON'T BE
SO LUCKY WITH ME.

00:03:48.414 --> 00:03:51.450
COME TO THINK OF IT,
SHOULDN'T THERE BE TWO OF YOU?

00:03:51.518 --> 00:03:54.420
THE PRIME SENATOR
SAID YOU HAD A PARTNER.

00:03:54.487 --> 00:03:56.523
I GUESS,
IF HE'S NOT HERE WITH YOU,

00:03:56.590 --> 00:04:00.927
THAT MEANS HE'S OFF SOMEWHERE
KEEPING LITTLE ALICE BUSY.

00:04:00.994 --> 00:04:02.962
Eugeo: YEAH, HE PROBABLY IS.

00:04:03.029 --> 00:04:05.264
I'M READY.

00:04:05.331 --> 00:04:06.766
LET'S GET THIS OVER WITH.

00:04:06.833 --> 00:04:09.836
I'M CURIOUS TO SEE
WHO'LL AVENGE YOU.

00:04:09.903 --> 00:04:11.304
( Bercouli chuckles )

00:04:11.370 --> 00:04:15.141
NO ONE, KID.
I DON'T HAVE A MENTOR.

00:04:15.208 --> 00:04:17.877
♪♪

00:04:25.852 --> 00:04:28.321
Eugeo: NORKIA STYLE,
LIGHTNING SLASH.

00:04:28.387 --> 00:04:30.690
OR IT'S SOMETHING LIKE IT.

00:04:30.757 --> 00:04:33.192
WITH HIS SWORD LIKE THAT,
IT'LL TAKE HIM

00:04:33.259 --> 00:04:35.695
AN EXTRA MOVE OR TWO
TO ACTIVATE THE TECHNIQUE,

00:04:35.762 --> 00:04:39.398
BUT IF I USE
THE AINCRAD STYLE'S SONIC LEAP,

00:04:39.465 --> 00:04:41.367
I CAN STRIKE HIM FIRST.

00:04:43.002 --> 00:04:45.572
Bercouli: AH, NOW,
THAT'S AN INTERESTING STANCE.

00:04:45.639 --> 00:04:47.941
I'VE NEVER SEEN IT BEFORE.

00:04:48.007 --> 00:04:49.743
DO YOU USE COMBO ATTACKS?

00:04:50.844 --> 00:04:52.011
Eugeo: MAYBE I DO.

00:04:52.078 --> 00:04:53.112
MAYBE I DON'T.

00:04:53.179 --> 00:04:54.648
WHY DO YOU CARE?

00:04:54.714 --> 00:04:57.050
Bercouli: I DON'T. IT'S JUST
THAT THERE WAS A KNIGHT

00:04:57.116 --> 00:05:00.486
FROM THE DARK TERRITORY
WHO LIKED TO USE 'EM, TOO.

00:05:00.554 --> 00:05:03.022
I FOUGHT HIM
A COUPLE OF TIMES BEFORE.

00:05:03.089 --> 00:05:06.125
I DIDN'T LIKE THE EXPERIENCE,
TO BE HONEST.

00:05:06.192 --> 00:05:07.961
MY STYLE'S SIMPLE.

00:05:08.027 --> 00:05:11.731
DOING ALL THEM FLASHY MOVES
IS WAY TOO COMPLICATED.

00:05:11.798 --> 00:05:15.368
Eugeo: IS THAT SO? DO YOU
WANT ME TO FIGHT LIKE YOU, THEN,

00:05:15.434 --> 00:05:17.470
USING ONLY CONVENTIONAL MOVES?

00:05:17.537 --> 00:05:21.407
Bercouli: HELL, NO. YOU WANNA
USE COMBO ATTACKS, GO AHEAD.

00:05:21.474 --> 00:05:24.143
I CAN HANDLE
ANYTHING YOU DISH OUT, KID.

00:05:24.210 --> 00:05:26.312
I SHOULD WARN YOU, THOUGH,

00:05:26.379 --> 00:05:29.048
I'M GONNA USE
MY BEST MOVE FIRST,

00:05:29.115 --> 00:05:31.317
AND YOU AIN'T READY FOR IT.

00:05:32.185 --> 00:05:33.753
( Eugeo gasps )

00:05:33.820 --> 00:05:36.623
IF HIS SWORD'S
ALREADY IN PERFECT CONTROL,

00:05:36.690 --> 00:05:38.758
THEN I'VE ONLY GOT ONE CHANCE.

00:05:38.825 --> 00:05:43.062
AS HE ACTIVATES HIS MOVE,
I'LL ATTACK WITH SONIC LEAP.

00:05:43.129 --> 00:05:47.501
Bercouli: TASTE THE BLADE
OF BERCOULI SYNTHESIS ONE.

00:05:48.702 --> 00:05:50.136
EN GARDE.

00:05:50.203 --> 00:05:51.605
Eugeo: BERCOULI?

00:05:51.671 --> 00:05:52.906
♪♪

00:05:52.972 --> 00:05:54.808
( chorus vocalizing )

00:05:54.874 --> 00:05:55.842
( Bercouli grunts )

00:05:55.909 --> 00:05:57.944
( ticking clock slows )

00:05:58.011 --> 00:06:00.446
( Eugeo yelling )

00:06:02.081 --> 00:06:03.382
( ticking clock slows )

00:06:03.449 --> 00:06:06.252
( gasps ) THAT RIPPLE,

00:06:06.319 --> 00:06:08.087
IT'S WHERE HE JUST SLASHED.

00:06:11.124 --> 00:06:12.559
( groans )

00:06:20.299 --> 00:06:22.368
( gasping )

00:06:26.039 --> 00:06:29.042
Bercouli: OOF.
TALK ABOUT CUTTING IT CLOSE.

00:06:29.108 --> 00:06:30.443
THE LAST THING I EXPECTED

00:06:30.510 --> 00:06:33.613
WAS FOR YOU TO COME
RUSHING IN AT ME LIKE THAT.

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:37.383
SORRY, KID.
I DAMN NEAR KILLED YOU.

00:06:37.385 --> 00:06:41.022
Eugeo: YEAH, I KNOW YOU DID,
BUT WITH WHAT?

00:06:41.089 --> 00:06:45.193
Bercouli: THAT WAS MY BEST MOVE,
JUST LIKE I TOLD YOU.

00:06:45.260 --> 00:06:48.864
WHEN I TOOK THAT SWING,
I WASN'T JUST SLICING AIR.

00:06:48.930 --> 00:06:53.201
I WAS SLICING A MOMENT
IN THE FUTURE, SO TO SPEAK.

00:06:53.268 --> 00:06:56.037
Eugeo: SLICING THE FUTURE?

00:06:56.104 --> 00:06:59.541
Bercouli: THE FIRST TIME I SAW
A DARK KNIGHT USE A COMBO ATTACK

00:06:59.608 --> 00:07:03.144
WAS JUST AFTER I BECAME
AN INTEGRITY KNIGHT MYSELF.

00:07:03.211 --> 00:07:06.782
THE SWORD TECHNIQUES I LEARNED
WERE ALL ABOUT PUTTING

00:07:06.848 --> 00:07:10.085
AS MUCH STRENGTH AS I COULD
BEHIND A SINGLE STRIKE,

00:07:10.151 --> 00:07:13.522
BUT SWORD TECHNIQUES
USING COMBINATION MOVES

00:07:13.589 --> 00:07:16.057
FOCUS ON HOW TO HANDLE
YOUR ENEMY'S ATTACKS

00:07:16.124 --> 00:07:17.859
AND LAND HITS.

00:07:17.926 --> 00:07:22.163
IT'S PRETTY OBVIOUS WHICH
IS MORE PRACTICAL IN A FIGHT.

00:07:22.230 --> 00:07:26.334
ANYWAY, I GOT BEAT UP REAL GOOD,
BUT I SURVIVED.

00:07:26.401 --> 00:07:27.836
THEN I GOT TO THINKING

00:07:27.903 --> 00:07:30.906
HOW I COULD LAND A HIT
AGAINST A COMBO USER.

00:07:32.473 --> 00:07:34.710
I FOUND THE ANSWER
WITH THIS THING.

00:07:34.776 --> 00:07:39.781
ORIGINALLY IT WAS PART OF
A DIVINE OBJECT CALLED A CLOCK.

00:07:39.848 --> 00:07:43.519
IT USED TO HANG ON THE WALL
OF THE CENTRAL CATHEDRAL.

00:07:43.585 --> 00:07:46.522
IT WAS HERE WHEN THE WORLD
WAS FIRST CREATED,

00:07:46.588 --> 00:07:48.624
OR SO I WAS TOLD.

00:07:50.191 --> 00:07:51.660
IT HAD A WEIRD NAME.

00:07:51.727 --> 00:07:54.262
THE PONTIFEX
CALLED IT "SYSTEM CLOCK"

00:07:54.329 --> 00:07:55.797
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

00:07:55.864 --> 00:07:58.634
WHEN LITTLE ALICE
USES HER OSMANTHUS BLADE,

00:07:58.700 --> 00:08:01.737
IT CUTS THROUGH
THE HORIZONTAL AXIS OF SPACE,

00:08:01.803 --> 00:08:04.840
BUT MINE CUTS
THE VERTICAL AXIS OF TIME.

00:08:06.341 --> 00:08:08.343
NOW IT'S GOT A NEW NAME,

00:08:08.409 --> 00:08:10.646
THE TIME‐SPLITTING SWORD.

00:08:11.513 --> 00:08:12.648
Eugeo: WHEN HE SWUNG IT,

00:08:12.714 --> 00:08:14.916
THE FORCE OF HIS STRIKE
STAYED IN PLACE.

00:08:14.983 --> 00:08:18.019
THAT MEANS I DON'T HAVE
A CHANCE AGAINST HIM UP CLOSE.

00:08:19.521 --> 00:08:21.523
I'LL HAVE TO USE
LONG‐RANGE ATTACKS.

00:08:21.590 --> 00:08:24.159
SYSTEM CALL. CONNECT ARMAMENT.

00:08:24.225 --> 00:08:26.061
‐ SEARCH ARCHIVED MEMORY.
‐ Bercouli: LET ME GUESS.

00:08:26.127 --> 00:08:29.430
YOU'RE SETTING YOURSELF UP TO
ATTACK FROM A DISTANCE, RIGHT?

00:08:29.497 --> 00:08:32.568
EVERYONE WHO SEES
THAT MOVE DOES.

00:08:32.634 --> 00:08:35.036
SAME GOES FOR ALL
THE INTEGRITY KNIGHTS

00:08:35.103 --> 00:08:38.740
THAT CAME AFTER ME,
INCLUDING FANATIO AND ALICE.

00:08:38.807 --> 00:08:40.576
ONCE THEY SAW THAT MOVE,

00:08:40.642 --> 00:08:42.578
THEY PICKED
LONG‐RANGE PERFECT CONTROL

00:08:42.644 --> 00:08:44.445
TO TRY AND DEAL WITH IT.

00:08:44.513 --> 00:08:45.681
I CAN'T BLAME 'EM.

00:08:45.747 --> 00:08:47.448
TRYING TO BRING ME DOWN

00:08:47.516 --> 00:08:50.251
GOT TO BE SORT OF
A CONTEST BETWEEN 'EM.

00:08:50.318 --> 00:08:53.354
BUT I NEVER LOST.
I SPARRED WITH ALL OF 'EM,

00:08:53.421 --> 00:08:55.991
AND HERE I AM,
STILL THEIR COMMANDER.

00:08:58.860 --> 00:09:01.763
WELL, IF ONE OF 'EM
DOES TAKE MY JOB,

00:09:01.830 --> 00:09:03.765
IT'LL PROBABLY BE ALICE.

00:09:03.832 --> 00:09:06.968
I SURE AM LOOKIN' FORWARD
TO THIS, THOUGH.

00:09:07.035 --> 00:09:09.370
I'M CURIOUS TO SEE
WHAT KIND OF MOVES

00:09:09.437 --> 00:09:12.207
HELPED YOU GET PAST
ALL THOSE KNIGHTS.

00:09:12.273 --> 00:09:14.743
Eugeo: DON'T WORRY. YOU WILL.

00:09:15.644 --> 00:09:17.112
( Bercouli chuckles )

00:09:17.178 --> 00:09:18.980
COME AND GET IT, KID.

00:09:19.047 --> 00:09:22.918
THIS TIME,
I WON'T GO EASY ON YOU.

00:09:28.423 --> 00:09:30.926
Eugeo: ENHANCE ARMAMENT!

00:09:30.992 --> 00:09:33.662
♪♪

00:09:38.700 --> 00:09:39.835
( Bercouli grunts )

00:09:48.243 --> 00:09:49.344
( Eugeo yells )

00:09:49.410 --> 00:09:50.579
( Bercouli yells )

00:09:50.646 --> 00:09:52.180
( ticking clock slows )

00:09:52.247 --> 00:09:54.550
( gasps )

00:09:54.616 --> 00:09:57.686
( Eugeo roars )

00:10:00.088 --> 00:10:01.690
( Bercouli yelps )

00:10:05.493 --> 00:10:06.461
( Eugeo grunts )

00:10:06.528 --> 00:10:07.996
( ice shatters )

00:10:12.267 --> 00:10:13.201
( Bercouli gasps )

00:10:17.238 --> 00:10:18.507
CLEVER.

00:10:18.574 --> 00:10:20.809
( Eugeo roars )

00:10:22.511 --> 00:10:24.513
BLUE ROSE SWORD...

00:10:24.580 --> 00:10:26.481
LEND ME YOUR POWER.

00:10:26.548 --> 00:10:29.184
RELEASE RECOLLECTION!

00:10:35.526 --> 00:10:37.160
Cardinal:
NOW PAY CLOSE ATTENTION.

00:10:37.227 --> 00:10:40.397
THE PERFECT WEAPON CONTROL ART
HAS TWO STAGES,

00:10:40.463 --> 00:10:42.465
ENHANCE AND RELEASE.

00:10:42.533 --> 00:10:43.934
Kirito: ENHANCE?

00:10:44.001 --> 00:10:46.169
‐ Eugeo: RELEASE?
‐ Cardinal: YES.

00:10:46.236 --> 00:10:50.240
ENHANCING AWAKENS
PART OF YOUR WEAPON'S MEMORIES.

00:10:50.307 --> 00:10:53.644
THE ACT CAUSES
A NEW ATTACK TO MANIFEST.

00:10:53.711 --> 00:10:55.178
IN THE RELEASING STAGE,

00:10:55.245 --> 00:10:58.048
YOU CAN AWAKEN
ALL OF YOUR WEAPON'S MEMORIES.

00:10:58.115 --> 00:11:01.151
THEN YOU CAN UNLEASH
ITS MOST SAVAGE POWER.

00:11:01.218 --> 00:11:03.086
Kirito: OH. I GET IT.

00:11:03.153 --> 00:11:04.688
♪♪

00:11:08.291 --> 00:11:11.962
THAT EXPLAINS ELDRIE'S WHIP.
IN ITS ENHANCED STAGE,

00:11:12.029 --> 00:11:14.998
IT CAN GET LONGER THAN NORMAL
AND THEN SPLIT.

00:11:15.065 --> 00:11:17.234
♪♪

00:11:19.637 --> 00:11:21.471
Eugeo: THEN ITS RELEASE STAGE

00:11:21.539 --> 00:11:23.507
WAS WHEN IT CHANGED
INTO A SNAKE.

00:11:23.574 --> 00:11:25.876
Cardinal: YOU ARE CORRECT.
THAT SAID,

00:11:25.943 --> 00:11:28.879
YOU TWO SHOULD AVOID USING
RELEASE FOR THE TIME BEING.

00:11:28.946 --> 00:11:30.981
Eugeo: WH‐WHY SHOULD WE?

00:11:31.048 --> 00:11:33.483
Cardinal: BECAUSE YOU ARE
NOT YET READY TO.

00:11:33.551 --> 00:11:35.886
YOU HAVE ONLY
JUST LEARNED OF THE ART.

00:11:35.953 --> 00:11:38.188
UNTIL YOU MASTER IT,
YOU CANNOT CONTROL

00:11:38.255 --> 00:11:41.124
THE POWER GENERATED
BY YOUR WEAPON'S MEMORIES,

00:11:41.191 --> 00:11:44.695
ESPECIALLY THOSE
OF A DIVINE OBJECT LIKE YOURS.

00:11:44.762 --> 00:11:47.631
IT CAN HARM YOU
AS MUCH AS YOUR ENEMY.

00:11:47.698 --> 00:11:51.669
IF YOU'RE NOT CAREFUL,
IT WILL KILL YOU.

00:11:51.735 --> 00:11:53.871
( ice crackling )

00:11:57.808 --> 00:11:58.909
( Eugeo chuckles )

00:11:58.976 --> 00:12:01.078
( Bercouli gasps, chuckles )

00:12:01.144 --> 00:12:05.683
I NEVER SAW A SWORDSMAN TOSS
HIS BLADE DURING A FIGHT BEFORE.

00:12:05.749 --> 00:12:08.185
DID YOU COME UP
WITH THAT TRICK YOURSELF?

00:12:08.251 --> 00:12:11.655
Eugeo: UH‐UH.
MY PARTNER TAUGHT ME THAT ONE.

00:12:11.722 --> 00:12:14.758
THE BATTLEFIELD
HAS LOTS OF OPPORTUNITIES.

00:12:14.825 --> 00:12:16.927
ANYTHING CAN BE
A WEAPON OR A TRAP.

00:12:16.994 --> 00:12:18.095
( Bercouli chuckles )

00:12:18.161 --> 00:12:21.231
MAKE THE BEST
OF WHAT YOU GOT. SMART.

00:12:21.298 --> 00:12:24.568
WELL, YOU MIGHT HAVE GOTTEN
THE UPPER HAND THIS ROUND,

00:12:24.635 --> 00:12:28.005
BUT THERE'S NO WAY IN HELL
YOU'RE GONNA BEAT ME!

00:12:28.071 --> 00:12:29.372
♪♪

00:12:29.439 --> 00:12:31.141
( growling )

00:12:31.208 --> 00:12:32.876
( roars )

00:12:35.879 --> 00:12:37.848
‐ ( Eugeo gasps )
‐ ( Bercouli chuckles )

00:12:40.884 --> 00:12:44.855
Eugeo: THE BLUE ROSE SWORD
HAS TWO DORMANT MEMORIES,

00:12:44.922 --> 00:12:47.290
ETERNAL ICE AND ROSE.

00:12:47.357 --> 00:12:51.862
WHEN I ACTIVATE ETERNAL ICE,
IT FREEZES EVERYTHING.

00:12:51.929 --> 00:12:54.765
NOW I'LL SHOW YOU
WHAT ROSE CAN DO.

00:12:56.299 --> 00:12:58.769
BLUE ROSE, BLOOM!

00:13:02.205 --> 00:13:04.341
( Bercouli gasps )
WHAT'D YOU DO?!

00:13:04.407 --> 00:13:07.477
Eugeo: THE ROSES BLOOM
BY ABSORBING THE LIFE

00:13:07.545 --> 00:13:09.847
OF THOSE TRAPPED IN THE ICE.

00:13:10.881 --> 00:13:12.315
Bercouli: DAMN IT.

00:13:12.382 --> 00:13:13.551
YOU LITTLE PUNK.

00:13:13.617 --> 00:13:15.853
SO WAS THIS YOUR PLAN ALL ALONG,

00:13:15.919 --> 00:13:17.287
KILLING THE BOTH OF US?!

00:13:17.354 --> 00:13:19.089
Eugeo: NOT US. JUST YOU.

00:13:19.156 --> 00:13:23.727
YOU HAVE AN ADVANTAGE OVER ME
IN EVERY WAY, EXCEPT ONE.

00:13:23.794 --> 00:13:26.396
IT'S YOUR TOTAL AMOUNT
OF LIFE LEFT.

00:13:26.463 --> 00:13:28.198
BASED ON YOUR APPEARANCE,

00:13:28.265 --> 00:13:31.134
YOU BECAME AN INTEGRITY KNIGHT
IN YOUR FORTIES,

00:13:31.201 --> 00:13:34.572
SO YOUR LIFE VALUE
IS LOWER THAN MINE.

00:13:34.638 --> 00:13:39.109
I'M YOUNGER, AND MY LIFE VALUE
IS NEAR ITS PEAK.

00:13:39.176 --> 00:13:41.111
EVEN THOUGH YOU LANDED A HIT,

00:13:41.178 --> 00:13:44.114
THE LIFE I HAVE LEFT
IS STILL HIGHER THAN YOURS.

00:13:44.181 --> 00:13:46.183
THAT'S WHAT I HOPED, ANYWAY.

00:13:46.249 --> 00:13:49.152
Bercouli: KID, YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

00:13:49.219 --> 00:13:53.223
YOU JUST SAID I "BECAME"
AN INTEGRITY KNIGHT.

00:13:53.290 --> 00:13:55.125
A KNIGHT'S ALL I'VE EVER BEEN.

00:13:55.192 --> 00:13:57.327
I DIDN'T HAVE A LIFE
BEFORE I WAS SUMMONED.

00:13:57.394 --> 00:14:00.430
Eugeo: AND THAT'S THE PART OF
YOU PEOPLE I FIND SO DESPICABLE!

00:14:00.497 --> 00:14:03.601
YOU'VE FORGOTTEN
WHO YOU USED TO BE.

00:14:03.667 --> 00:14:05.302
YOU'RE LOYAL TO THE AXIOM CHURCH

00:14:05.368 --> 00:14:07.304
WITHOUT KNOWING
WHAT IT REALLY IS.

00:14:07.370 --> 00:14:09.740
YOU ACT LIKE YOU'RE
CHAMPIONS OF JUSTICE,

00:14:09.807 --> 00:14:12.475
BUT YOU UPHOLD CORRUPTION!

00:14:12.543 --> 00:14:14.578
YOU THINK YOU'RE HERE
BECAUSE THE PONTIFEX

00:14:14.645 --> 00:14:17.548
SUMMONED YOU FROM HEAVEN,
BUT THAT'S A LIE!

00:14:17.615 --> 00:14:19.550
YOU HAD A MOTHER.

00:14:19.617 --> 00:14:21.719
SHE'S THE ONE
WHO GAVE YOU THE NAME BERCOULI.

00:14:21.785 --> 00:14:24.254
YOU'RE HUMAN, JUST LIKE ME!

00:14:24.321 --> 00:14:25.288
( gasps )

00:14:25.355 --> 00:14:29.359
BERCOULI. IN MY VILLAGE,
THEY TELL STORIES

00:14:29.426 --> 00:14:31.595
ABOUT HOW MUCH
OF A HERO YOU WERE.

00:14:31.662 --> 00:14:34.565
( Bercouli gasps )
WHAT STORIES?

00:14:34.632 --> 00:14:36.199
Eugeo: THINK BACK.

00:14:36.266 --> 00:14:39.202
I'M SURE YOU'VE
SEEN THIS SWORD BEFORE.

00:14:41.271 --> 00:14:44.041
Bercouli:
YEAH, I HAVE, SOMEWHERE.

00:14:44.107 --> 00:14:47.044
RIGHT. YEARS AGO...

00:14:47.110 --> 00:14:50.147
IT WAS IN THE NEST
OF THE WHITE DRAGON.

00:14:50.213 --> 00:14:52.482
I SAW IT THERE
AFTER I KILLED IT.

00:14:52.550 --> 00:14:54.952
Eugeo: YOU KILLED THE DRAGON?

00:14:55.819 --> 00:14:57.888
I SAW ITS BONES...

00:14:57.955 --> 00:15:03.894
AND NOW‐‐NOW YOU SAY
THE ONE WHO KILLED IT WAS YOU?

00:15:03.961 --> 00:15:07.097
A DRAGON
THAT PROTECTED THE HUMAN REALM,

00:15:07.164 --> 00:15:09.266
THE ONE FROM YOUR OWN LEGEND.

00:15:09.332 --> 00:15:12.603
DON'T YOU REMEMBER
ANYTHING ABOUT YOUR PAST,

00:15:12.670 --> 00:15:14.471
ABOUT WHO YOU WERE?

00:15:14.538 --> 00:15:18.709
IN RULID, THE VILLAGE YOU
FOUNDED AND WHERE I WAS BORN,

00:15:18.776 --> 00:15:20.177
EVERYONE KNEW ABOUT YOU.

00:15:20.243 --> 00:15:23.146
YOUNG OR OLD,
WE LOOKED UP TO YOU AS A HERO.

00:15:23.213 --> 00:15:26.449
BUT THE PONTIFEX
SEALED AWAY YOUR MEMORIES.

00:15:26.517 --> 00:15:30.988
SHE TURNED YOU
INTO THE FIRST INTEGRITY KNIGHT.

00:15:31.054 --> 00:15:32.590
THEN CAME THE OTHERS,

00:15:32.656 --> 00:15:37.628
EVERYONE FROM FANATIO TO ELDRIE,
EVEN ALICE,

00:15:37.695 --> 00:15:39.362
ALL OF YOU.

00:15:39.429 --> 00:15:42.900
BEFORE YOU BECAME
INTEGRITY KNIGHTS,

00:15:42.966 --> 00:15:44.034
YOU HAD LIVES.

00:15:44.101 --> 00:15:45.736
YOU WERE HUMAN.

00:15:45.803 --> 00:15:49.607
Bercouli:
SEALED AWAY MY MEMORIES?

00:15:49.673 --> 00:15:55.746
I CAN'T JUST BELIEVE
A WILD STORY LIKE THAT.

00:15:55.813 --> 00:15:59.316
BUT ALL THAT STUFF I WAS TOLD

00:15:59.382 --> 00:16:02.986
ABOUT ME BEING SUMMONED
FROM HEAVEN,

00:16:03.053 --> 00:16:07.357
I HAD MY DOUBTS FOR A WHILE NOW.

00:16:07.424 --> 00:16:09.492
( Eugeo shudders )

00:16:14.665 --> 00:16:16.834
‐ ( bouncing )
‐ ( laughing )

00:16:16.900 --> 00:16:19.202
♪♪

00:16:24.274 --> 00:16:28.679
Man: WELL, WELL!
NOW, WHAT DO WE HAVE HERE?

00:16:29.847 --> 00:16:30.781
( chuckles )

00:16:30.848 --> 00:16:33.684
( laughing )

00:16:34.752 --> 00:16:37.087
THIS WON'T DO. NO, NO, NO.

00:16:37.154 --> 00:16:39.890
THIS WON'T DO AT ALL,
MY DEAR COMMANDER.

00:16:39.957 --> 00:16:44.528
SURELY, GOOD SIR, YOU DON'T PLAN
TO DIE ON US LIKE THIS?

00:16:44.595 --> 00:16:47.798
THAT WOULD BE TREASON
AGAINST HER EMINENCE,

00:16:47.865 --> 00:16:50.467
THE LOVELY PONTIFEX.

00:16:50.534 --> 00:16:52.870
IF SHE WERE AWAKE
TO SEE YOU IN THIS STATE,

00:16:52.936 --> 00:16:54.237
SHE WOULD BE LIVID.

00:16:54.304 --> 00:16:58.075
Bercouli:
PRIME SENATOR CHUDELKIN,

00:16:58.141 --> 00:17:01.311
THIS IS A FIGHT
BETWEEN SWORDSMEN.

00:17:01.378 --> 00:17:04.748
A PIG LIKE YOU
HAS NO BUSINESS HERE.

00:17:04.815 --> 00:17:06.517
Chudelkin: HA HA HA!

00:17:06.584 --> 00:17:09.853
AFTER GOING SO EASY
ON THIS HERETIC,

00:17:09.920 --> 00:17:12.322
YOU HAVE NO BUSINESS
CORRECTING ME.

00:17:12.389 --> 00:17:15.192
DEAR COMMANDER, PRAY TELL,

00:17:15.258 --> 00:17:17.861
WHY DID YOU NOT USE
YOUR SWORD'S FULL POWER?

00:17:17.928 --> 00:17:21.298
IF YOU HAD, YOU COULD HAVE
SLAUGHTERED THIS LOATHSOME BRAT

00:17:21.364 --> 00:17:23.734
BEFORE HE OPENED
HIS SLANDEROUS LITTLE MOUTH.

00:17:23.801 --> 00:17:26.003
BUT YOU DID NOT, AND, THEREFORE,

00:17:26.069 --> 00:17:28.305
COMMITTED TREASON
AGAINST THE GLORIOUS PONTIFEX.

00:17:28.371 --> 00:17:30.440
‐ Bercouli: SHUT YOUR MOUTH.
‐ ( Chudelkin gasps )

00:17:30.508 --> 00:17:35.212
Bercouli: I FOUGHT
WITH EVERYTHING I HAD.

00:17:36.113 --> 00:17:38.215
BUT YOU LIED TO ME.

00:17:38.281 --> 00:17:41.284
YOU LIED TO ALL OF US.

00:17:41.351 --> 00:17:47.124
THIS KID AIN'T NO ASSASSIN
FROM THE DARK TERRITORY.

00:17:47.190 --> 00:17:50.894
AND COMPARED TO AN UGLY
PIECE OF SHIT LIKE YOU‐‐

00:17:50.961 --> 00:17:52.095
Chudelkin: SILENCE!

00:17:52.162 --> 00:17:54.665
BE SILENT, OR I'LL
RIP OFF YOUR HEAD!

00:17:56.199 --> 00:17:58.736
FOR YOUR INFORMATION, MY DEAR,

00:17:58.802 --> 00:18:00.270
WE WOULDN'T HAVE THIS PROBLEM

00:18:00.337 --> 00:18:03.306
IF YOU DAMNED KNIGHTS
WEREN'T SO DAMNED USELESS.

00:18:03.373 --> 00:18:06.276
HONESTLY,
WHEN HER EMINENCE AWAKES,

00:18:06.343 --> 00:18:08.679
YOU KNIGHTS WILL BE
THOROUGHLY PUNISHED.

00:18:08.746 --> 00:18:11.749
AT THE VERY LEAST, YOU AND
YOUR PRECIOUS VICE COMMANDER

00:18:11.815 --> 00:18:13.717
SHALL BE REPROCESSED.

00:18:13.784 --> 00:18:15.218
Bercouli: "RE‐" WHAT?

00:18:15.285 --> 00:18:17.821
YOU'RE TALKIN' OUT
YOUR ASS AGAIN.

00:18:17.888 --> 00:18:19.022
( Chudelkin chuckles )

00:18:19.089 --> 00:18:21.959
SYSTEM CALL! DEEP FREEZE!

00:18:22.025 --> 00:18:27.297
INTEGRATOR UNIT I.D.
ZERO‐ZERO‐ONE!

00:18:30.934 --> 00:18:32.803
( Bercouli gasps )

00:18:35.873 --> 00:18:37.174
( Eugeo gasping )

00:18:39.042 --> 00:18:41.444
( Chudelkin laughs )

00:18:41.512 --> 00:18:44.081
WE DON'T NEED
OLD FARTS LIKE NUMBER ONE

00:18:44.147 --> 00:18:46.449
STINKING UP THE PLACE ANYMORE.

00:18:46.517 --> 00:18:48.586
NOW WE HAVE A MUCH YOUNGER,

00:18:48.652 --> 00:18:50.353
‐ MORE USEFUL PAWN...
‐ Eugeo: KIRITO.

00:18:50.420 --> 00:18:52.590
Chudelkin: AT OUR DISPOSAL.

00:18:52.656 --> 00:18:54.291
Eugeo: ALICE.

00:18:56.527 --> 00:18:57.494
Kirito: EUGEO.

00:18:57.561 --> 00:18:59.396
Alice: IS SOMETHING THE MATTER?

00:18:59.462 --> 00:19:02.065
Kirito: HUH? OH, NO. NOTHING.

00:19:02.132 --> 00:19:03.734
AS SOON AS THE MOON COMES OUT,

00:19:03.801 --> 00:19:06.403
I THINK WE CAN START
CLIMBING UP THE WALL AGAIN.

00:19:06.469 --> 00:19:08.071
LONG AS I CAN MAKE SPIKES,

00:19:08.138 --> 00:19:10.140
IT SHOULD GO PRETTY EASY
FROM HERE ON.

00:19:10.207 --> 00:19:12.309
THERE'S NO MINIONS ABOVE US,

00:19:12.375 --> 00:19:14.578
AND THE OTHERS HERE
AIN'T WAKING UP.

00:19:14.645 --> 00:19:17.515
FOR NOW. BESIDES THE LACK
OF SACRED POWER,

00:19:17.581 --> 00:19:19.917
THE ONLY OTHER BIG PROBLEM
IS FOOD.

00:19:19.983 --> 00:19:22.285
I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU,
BUT I'M STARVING.

00:19:22.352 --> 00:19:24.822
IF I THINK ABOUT
HOW MUCH FURTHER WE GOTTA GO,

00:19:24.888 --> 00:19:26.223
MY HEAD STARTS SPINNING.

00:19:26.289 --> 00:19:29.026
Alice: COULD YOU BE
ANY MORE OF A DISAPPOINTMENT?

00:19:29.092 --> 00:19:30.160
Kirito: WHAT?!

00:19:30.227 --> 00:19:31.662
Alice: WHETHER WE MISS
A MEAL OR TWO

00:19:31.729 --> 00:19:34.732
IS THE LEAST OF OUR WORRIES,
UNLESS YOU ARE A CHILD.

00:19:34.798 --> 00:19:37.601
Kirito: YEAH, WELL,
TECHNICALLY, I STILL SORT OF AM.

00:19:37.668 --> 00:19:39.770
I MIGHT NOT ACT
LIKE IT ALL THE TIME,

00:19:39.837 --> 00:19:42.172
BUT I'M NOT EVEN
OUT OF MY TEENS YET.

00:19:42.239 --> 00:19:44.174
I DON'T EAT, MY LIFE GOES DOWN,

00:19:44.241 --> 00:19:46.109
A PROBLEM
YOU BADASS KNIGHTS DON'T HAVE.

00:19:46.176 --> 00:19:47.611
Alice: SUCH LANGUAGE!

00:19:47.678 --> 00:19:50.147
EVEN INTEGRITY KNIGHTS
GET HUNGRY.

00:19:50.213 --> 00:19:52.516
WE MUST EAT,
OR WE LOSE LIFE LIKE YOU.

00:19:52.583 --> 00:19:54.451
‐ ( stomach grumbles )
‐ ( both gasp )

00:19:56.186 --> 00:19:57.120
( Kirito snickers )

00:19:57.187 --> 00:19:58.421
WHOA! HOLD ON!

00:19:58.488 --> 00:20:00.090
SORRY! I WAS KIDDING!

00:20:00.157 --> 00:20:04.294
OF COURSE YOU GET HUNGRY.
YOU'RE AS ALIVE AS ANYONE ELSE.

00:20:04.361 --> 00:20:07.731
SPEAKIN' OF FOOD,
WHERE ARE CARDINAL'S SNACKS?

00:20:07.798 --> 00:20:08.832
Alice: HMM?

00:20:08.899 --> 00:20:12.102
Kirito: AW, YEAH.
I KNEW I SNAGGED SOME MORE.

00:20:12.169 --> 00:20:13.637
LOOKIT! IT'S DINNERTIME!

00:20:13.704 --> 00:20:15.105
♪♪

00:20:15.172 --> 00:20:16.540
Alice: WHY IN THE WORLD

00:20:16.607 --> 00:20:19.009
WOULD YOU STORE YOUR FOOD
IN SUCH A WAY?

00:20:19.076 --> 00:20:22.179
Kirito: I DON'T. I JUST TAPPED
MY POCKET, AND THERE THEY WERE.

00:20:22.245 --> 00:20:24.081
TRY IT SOMETIME.

00:20:24.147 --> 00:20:26.517
BUT FIRST I GOTTA
GET THESE READY TO EAT.

00:20:26.584 --> 00:20:27.350
( chuckles )

00:20:27.417 --> 00:20:28.418
( Alice groans )

00:20:28.485 --> 00:20:30.253
Kirito: SYSTEM CALL.

00:20:30.320 --> 00:20:32.690
GENERATE THERMAL ELEMENT.

00:20:32.756 --> 00:20:33.691
BURST ELE‐‐

00:20:33.757 --> 00:20:34.858
Alice: NO, YOU FOOL!

00:20:34.925 --> 00:20:36.193
Kirito: WHAT?

00:20:36.259 --> 00:20:38.729
Alice: IF YOU USE THAT ART,
YOU WILL BURN THEM!

00:20:38.796 --> 00:20:40.497
Kirito: SORRY.

00:20:40.564 --> 00:20:42.265
( gasps )

00:20:44.502 --> 00:20:47.037
Alice: GENERATE THERMAL ELEMENT,

00:20:47.104 --> 00:20:48.906
AQUEOUS ELEMENT,

00:20:48.972 --> 00:20:50.841
AERIAL ELEMENT.

00:20:52.275 --> 00:20:55.579
VORTEX SHAPE. BURST.

00:20:56.446 --> 00:20:58.148
( steam hissing )

00:20:58.215 --> 00:20:59.950
Kirito: WHOA!

00:21:00.017 --> 00:21:01.084
HURRY! GIMME ONE!

00:21:01.151 --> 00:21:02.820
( Alice chuckles )

00:21:02.886 --> 00:21:04.021
Kirito: WAIT! NO, NO, NO!

00:21:04.087 --> 00:21:05.388
Alice: I AM JOKING.

00:21:06.256 --> 00:21:07.958
( Kirito chuckles )

00:21:08.025 --> 00:21:09.960
( blows )

00:21:11.028 --> 00:21:12.329
MMM.

00:21:12.395 --> 00:21:14.231
THAT HIT THE SPOT.

00:21:14.297 --> 00:21:15.498
THANKS FOR SHOWING ME THAT.

00:21:15.566 --> 00:21:17.334
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU COULD STEAM FOOD

00:21:17.400 --> 00:21:18.802
USING ELEMENTS
INSTEAD OF A PAN.

00:21:18.869 --> 00:21:21.572
DID YOU TEACH
YOUR LITTLE SIS HOW TO COOK?

00:21:21.639 --> 00:21:23.707
'CAUSE SELKA'S
REALLY GOOD AT IT.

00:21:23.774 --> 00:21:24.608
( gasps )

00:21:24.675 --> 00:21:26.877
Alice: WHAT DID
YOU SAY JUST NOW?

00:21:26.944 --> 00:21:28.411
( Kirito gasps )

00:21:29.312 --> 00:21:31.782
THAT YOU HAVE A LITTLE SISTER.

00:21:31.849 --> 00:21:34.151
HER NAME'S SELKA.

00:21:34.217 --> 00:21:35.586
Alice: SISTER?

00:21:37.087 --> 00:21:39.723
♪♪

00:21:39.790 --> 00:21:41.124
( gasps )

00:21:41.191 --> 00:21:42.826
Kirito: I CAN
TELL YOU ABOUT HER.

00:21:42.893 --> 00:21:46.764
I CAN TELL YOU EVERYTHING
I KNOW ABOUT THIS PLACE.

00:21:46.830 --> 00:21:49.032
I DON'T KNOW
IF YOU'LL BELIEVE ME,

00:21:49.099 --> 00:21:50.500
BUT IT'S WORTH A SHOT.

00:21:51.969 --> 00:21:53.070
( Alice sighs )

00:21:53.136 --> 00:21:55.806
GO ON, THEN.

00:21:55.873 --> 00:21:56.940
HOWEVER...

00:21:57.007 --> 00:22:01.244
IF I DETECT EVEN
A TRACE OF DECEIT IN YOUR WORDS,

00:22:01.311 --> 00:22:04.014
I SHALL END YOUR LIFE.

00:22:04.081 --> 00:22:05.482
( Kirito gasps )